An **annuity** converts a lump sum corpus into a guaranteed monthly income for life (or a fixed period). Indian insurers offer annuity rates of 5.5–7% p.a. for immediate annuities, depending on the type (life annuity, joint life, with/without return of purchase price). NPS mandates 40% of corpus go into an annuity. This calculator helps you estimate the monthly pension.
